'''iPod'''&reg; (''plural'' '''iPods''')
{{wikipedia}}
#A brand of [[MP3 player]] manufactured by [[w:Apple Computer|Apple Computer]] that stores [[media]] on either a small [[hard drive]] or [[flash memory]]

There are various models of the iPod, including the ipod shuffle, nano, mini and the iPod itself.

All of the systems have a various memory size ranging from the shuffles miserly 256Mb to the iPod photos 60Gb. All ipods store and play music, but some can play videos and show pictures.  

